			<div id="body-content">

			<h1 class="entry-title">The evolving purpose of design</h1>

					

				

				<h2 class="subhead">Design is about communication and respect as much as function.</h2>

			
			

			<div class="entry-meta">				

				
					<span class="meta-sep">by</span> 	

					
						<span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" rel="author" href="http://radar.oreilly.com/gmartin" title="View all posts by Glen Martin">

						Glen Martin</a></span> |								

					
				<!-- RSPEAK_STOP -->

				
					<a href="http://twitter.com/GlenWM5440"> @GlenWM5440</a> |

				
				
					<a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/114119977885933637441/posts"> +Glen Martin</a> |

				
				
				
					<span class="comments-link utility-items"><a href="http://radar.oreilly.com/2014/04/the-evolving-purpose-of-design.html#comments" title="Comment on The evolving purpose of design"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="60120 http://radar.oreilly.com/?p=60120">Comment: 1</span></a></span>

					<span class="meta-sep utility-items"> | </span>

					

				
				<span class="entry-date">April 10, 2014</span> 				

			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

			

			<div class="entry-utility social">						

				<!-- AddThis Button BEGIN -->					

				<div class="utility-items addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style home  addthis_32x32_style" addthis:url="http://radar.oreilly.com/2014/04/the-evolving-purpose-of-design.html" addthis:title="The evolving purpose of design">					

					<a class="addthis_button_twitter"  addthis:url="http://radar.oreilly.com/2014/04/the-evolving-purpose-of-design.html" addthis:title="The evolving purpose of design"></a>						

					<a class="addthis_button_google_plusone_share" addthis:url="http://radar.oreilly.com/2014/04/the-evolving-purpose-of-design.html" addthis:title="The evolving purpose of design"></a>	

